%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Nvidia%20rolls%20back%202%20hot-button%20topics%20in%20a%20slimmer%20%E2%80%94%20and%20more%20China-focused%20%E2%80%94%20annual%20report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227230%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jensen%20Huang%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699fd891e8408f6671804ab6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224820%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENvidia's%20annual%20report%20was%20missing%20two%20sections%20it%20had%20last%20year.%3Cp%3EFabrice%20COFFRINI%20%2F%20AFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ENvidia's%20latest%20annual%20report%20omitted%20sections%20on%20climate%20change%20and%20DEI.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20report%20highlighted%20US%20chip%20export%20rules%20hindering%20Nvidia's%20competitiveness%20in%20China's%20market.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENvidia%20said%20its%20estimates%20for%20the%20current%20quarter%20don't%20include%20sales%20of%20data-center%20chips%20to%20China.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiggest-takeaways-from-nvidias-q4-earnings-vera-rubin-chips-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENvidia's%20annual%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20released%20Wednesday%2C%20came%20in%20leaner%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20chipmaker%20axed%20or%20trimmed%20sections%20on%20climate%20change%20and%20diversity%2C%20equity%2C%20and%20inclusion%20compared%20with%20last%20year's%20version.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%202025%20section%20titled%20%26quot%3Bsustainability%20and%20governance%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20delved%20into%20clean%20energy%20and%20emission%20commitments%2C%20was%20absent%20from%20Wednesday's%20report.%20That%20report%20mentioned%20sustainability%2C%20but%20in%20the%20context%20of%20Nvidia's%20business%20sustainability%20or%20adherence%20to%20sustainability-related%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20published%20last%20year%20read%3A%20%26quot%3BThese%20issues%20are%20important%20for%20our%20continued%20business%20success%20and%20reflect%20the%20topics%20of%20highest%20concern%20to%20Nvidia%20and%20our%20stakeholders.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENext%2C%20a%20section%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-salary-pay-engineer-product-manager-scientist-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehuman%20capital%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewas%20significantly%20cut.%20In%202025%2C%20the%20company%20included%20subheadings%20such%20as%20%26quot%3BCompensation%2C%20Benefits%2C%20and%20Well-Being%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BDiversity%2C%20Inclusion%2C%20and%20Belonging%20at%20Nvidia.%26quot%3B%20Neither%20section%20was%20included%20this%20year%2C%20and%20the%20word%20diversity%20was%20not%20mentioned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDEI%20efforts%20were%20summarized%20in%20one%20line%20this%20year%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20also%20utilize%20employee%20listening%20systems%20to%20gather%20feedback%20and%20maintain%20an%20inclusive%20culture%20where%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-employee-jensen-huang-leadership-lessons-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehiring%20and%20promotions%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20based%20on%20merit.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-day-one-agenda-executive-orders-inauguration-day-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Esigned%20an%20executive%20order%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20end%20diversity%20programs%20across%20the%20federal%20government%20and%20ordered%20all%20federal%20DEI%20staffers%20to%20be%20placed%20on%20leave%20while%20their%20departments%20were%20disbanded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20move%20that%20made%20waves%20in%20the%20private%20sector%20as%20well.%20Tech%20companies%20such%20as%20Microsoft%2C%20Meta%2C%20and%20Salesforce%20cut%20DEI%20programs.%20However%2C%20some%20companies%2C%20including%20Costco%2C%20have%20publicly%20defended%20their%20diversity%20initiatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider%20about%20this%20year's%20changes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228d21cf30-b78a-41ca-b8d3-023ef05cb706%5C%22%3EChina%20focus%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAt%2093%20pages%2C%20Nvidia's%20latest%20annual%20report%20was%20about%2040%20pages%20shorter%20than%20last%20year's.%20Still%2C%20China%20got%20more%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eairtime.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBesides%20recapping%20the%20US%20government's%20chip%20export%20restrictions%20on%20China%2C%20Nvidia%20wrote%20that%20under%20the%20current%20rules%2C%20it%20cannot%20deliver%20a%20competitive%20product%20for%20the%20Chinese%20data%20center%20market.%20The%20company%20added%20that%20this%20allowed%20rivals%20to%20build%20larger%20customer%20bases%20worldwide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20lost%20opportunity%20and%20the%20benefit%20to%20our%20competitors%20will%20have%20a%20material%20and%20adverse%20impact%20on%20our%20business%2C%20operating%20results%2C%20and%20financial%20condition%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20said%20its%20estimates%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-q4-earnings-live-updates-ai-chips-rubin-jensen-huang-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20current%20quarter%20%3C%2Fa%3Edid%20not%20include%20any%20expected%20revenue%20from%20sales%20of%20data-center%20chips%20to%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20Nvidia%20reported%20better-than-expected%20fiscal%20year%202026%20earnings%2C%20owing%20to%20strong%20AI%20data%20center%20demand.%20It%20reported%20%2468.1%20billion%20in%20revenue%2C%20a%2073%25%20year-over-year%20increase%2C%20and%20about%20%2443%20billion%20in%20profits%2C%2094%25%20higher%20than%20the%20same%20time%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20chipmaker's%20stock%20was%20up%20slightly%20after%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-annual-report-dei-climate-change-focuses-china-2026-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772088619000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699fd97b50f42603b0f8ef19%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-annual-report-dei-climate-change-focuses-china-2026-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20report%20highlighted%20US%20chip%20export%20rules%20hindering%20Nvidia's%20competitiveness%20in%20China's%20market.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sgoel%40insider.com%20(Shubhangi%20Goel)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-annual-report-dei-climate-change-focuses-china-2026-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jay%20Z%20and%20Beyonce%20cancel%20plans%20to%20shift%20to%20the%20UK%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772087864000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-128804644%2Cimgsize-3048.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fmusic%2Fnews%2Fjay-z-and-beyonces-uk-shift-thwarted-issues-with-property-causes-couple-to-back-out-for-now-report%2Farticleshow%2F128804644.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F128804644.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EMusic%20power%20couple%20Jay-Z%20and%20Beyonc%C3%A9%20have%20reportedly%20shelved%20their%20relocation%20plans%20to%20the%20UK%20after%20uncovering%20a%20major%20issue%20with%20their%20chosen%20property.%20The%207.5-million-euro%20Cotswolds%20mansion%20they%20were%20considering%20is%20said%20to%20be%20highly%20vulnerable%20to%20flooding%2C%20prompting%20them%20to%20rethink%20the%20move%E2%80%94especially%20in%20light%20of%20their%20recent%20experience%20with%20devasta