ss%20on%20her%20own%20terms%20%E2%80%94%20without%20a%20fixed%20finish%20line.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EI%20thought%20I%20was%20on%20track%20%E2%80%94%20until%20the%20year%20everything%20fell%20apart.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20weeks%20into%20January%202023%2C%20I%20was%20blindsided%20by%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdumped-on-birthday-over-text-european-family-vacation-healed-me-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eunexpected%20breakup%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20the%20months%20that%20followed%2C%20I%20moved%20through%20my%20days%20on%20autopilot%2C%20watching%20the%20year%20continue%20to%20unravel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20May%2C%20I%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flaid-off-amazon-employee-found-job-two-weeks-tech-advice-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elaid%20off%20from%20my%20job%3C%2Fa%3E%20coordinating%20large%20conferences%20and%20corporate%20travel.%20I%20took%20a%20position%20at%20a%20family-run%20wedding%20business%20that%20was%20building%20out%20its%20travel%20department.%20I%20told%20myself%20things%20were%20starting%20to%20look%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20between%20a%2090-minute%20commute%2C%20sitting%20at%20a%20desk%20all%20day%2C%20and%20performing%20mundane%20tasks%20not%20listed%20in%20my%20job%20description%2C%20I%20began%20to%20spiral%20instead%20of%20heal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlmost%20every%20day%2C%20I'd%20retreat%20to%20my%20car%20at%20lunchtime%20and%20break%20down%20in%20tears%2C%20overwhelmed%20by%20how%20unhappy%20I%20was.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22496fe499-3eb2-41db-b67f-4214588c9ad2%5C%22%3EThe%20%26quot%3BAmerican%20dream%26quot%3B%20began%20to%20feel%20like%20a%20trap%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20I%20was%20a%20kid%2C%20I'd%20treated%20success%20like%20a%20checklist%20built%20from%20American%20expectations%20I%20absorbed%20through%20school%2C%20TV%2C%20and%20social%20media.%20It%20seemed%20simple%20enough%3A%20Stay%20in%20line%20with%20peers%2C%20get%20married%20before%20turning%2030%2C%20and%20buy%20a%20big%20house%20to%20raise%20a%20family%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20becoming%20clear%20that%20this%20narrative%20might%20not%20align%20with%20the%20life%20I%20wanted%20for%20myself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELater%20that%20same%20year%2C%20I%20dealt%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsigns-of-bad-toxic-friends-how-to-deal-break-up-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etoxic%20roommate%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20serious%20health%20scare%20in%20my%20family%2C%20and%20a%20car%20accident.%20Then%2C%20just%20days%20before%20the%20New%20Year%2C%20I%20got%20one%20final%20surprise%3A%20another%20layoff.%20This%20time%2C%20however%2C%20I%20felt%20relief.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWalking%20out%20of%20that%20office%20for%20the%20last%20time%20allowed%20me%20to%20stop%20chasing%20a%20version%20of%20success%20I%20knew%20would%20never%20satisfy%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227e437439-c27c-42c3-8618-4080c930f002%5C%22%3EDistance%20changed%20the%20pressure%20I%20was%20living%20under%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%202024%20began%2C%20I%20set%20a%20clear%20goal%20for%20myself%20to%20sublet%20my%20apartment%2C%20sell%20my%20belongings%2C%20and%20board%20a%20one-way%20flight%20to%20South%20Korea%20by%20April%2015.%20My%20plan%20was%20to%20begin%20an%20eight-month%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftravel-southeast-asia-worst-best-cities-thailand-laos-vietnam-malaysia-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ejourney%20across%20Asia%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Australia.%20After%20four%20months%20of%20careful%20planning%2C%20I%20boarded%20that%20flight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStarting%20the%20trip%20with%20a%20friend%20in%20Seoul%20made%20the%20beginning%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%2015-hour%20flight%20over%20%E2%80%94%20feel%20safe%20and%20manageable.%20When%20she%20boarded%20her%20flight%20back%20to%20the%20US%2C%20and%20I%20headed%20off%20to%20Thailand%20alone%2C%20that%20distraction%20disappeared.%20I%20was%20officially%20left%20alone%20with%20my%20own%20thoughts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarly%20on%20in%20Southeast%20Asia%2C%20I%20questioned%20what%20I%20was%20doing%20and%20where%20it%20would%20all%20lead.%20I%20cried%20in%20hostels%20and%20had%20panic%20attacks%20on%20the%20back%20of%20motorbikes.%20My%20anxiety%20was%20triggered%20by%20the%20blasting%20music%20of%20Bangkok's%20Khao%20San%20Road%20and%20Ho%20Chi%20Minh%20City's%20endless%20traffic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Woman%20in%20red%2C%20wearing%20sunglasses%2C%20standing%20on%20Ha%20Giang%20Loop%2C%20northern%20Vietnam.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699e850a50f42603b0f8da6d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EStrum%20escaped%20the%20pressure%20she'd%20been%20living%20under%20while%20traveling%20through%20the%20mountains%20in%20northern%20Vietnam.%3Cp%3EProvided%20by%20Macie%20Strum%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20more%20I%20took%20note%20of%20my%20surroundings%2C%20the%20less%20the%20world%20around%20me%20matched%20the%20urgency%20in%20my%20head.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20traveled%20the%20Ha%20Giang%20Loop%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmotorbike-vietnam-ha-giang-loop-dangerous-roadtrip-worth-it-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENorthern%20Vietnam%20by%20motorbike%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20realized%20that%20my%20idea%20of%20success%20was%20built%20upon%20a%20level%20of%20pressure%20that%20didn't%20exist%20up%20in%20these%20Vietnamese%20mountains.%20Local%20life%20didn't%20revolve%20around%20strict%20deadlines%20and%20productivity%20scales.%20Instead%2C%20it%20centered%20on%20routine%2C%20family%2C%20and%20staying%20present%20each%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20moved%20through%20each%20country%2C%20I%20connected%20with%20travelers%20of%20every%20age%20and%20background%2C%20many%20of%20whom%20were%20unemployed%2C%20exploring%20new%20paths%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fwork-from-home%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eworking%20online%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20simply%20figuring%20things%20out%20as%20they%20went.%20Some%20were%20meticulous%20planners%3B%20others%20lived%20day%20to%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsoutheast-asia-travel-mistakes-packing-weather-clothing-traditions-medicine-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ejungles%20of%20Malaysian%20Borneo%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20met%20a%20fellow%20American%20who%20was%20also%20redefining%20her%20life%20after%20a%20heavy%20breakup.%20I%20remember%20the%20first%20night%20we%20met%2C%20we%20talked%20for%20hours%20about%20life%2C%20expectations%2C%20and%20the%20fear%20of%20what%20would%20come%20next.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20ended%20up%20traveling%20together%20to%20Kuala%20Lumpur%2C%20meeting%20again%20in%20Penang%2C%20and%20later%20in%20Bali.%20Seeing%20her%20in%20so%20many%20different%20places%20reminded%20me%20how%20many%20others%20were%20navigating%20the%20same%20uncertainty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20reframed%20my%20view%20of%20travel%20%E2%80%94%20not%20as%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgave-up-life-abroad-to-follow-partner-split-bad-idea-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebreak%20from%20real%20life%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%20as%20an%20active%20part%20of%20it.%20For%20the%20first%20time%2C%20uncertainty%20no%20longer%20felt%20like%20failure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20posing%20with%20the%20Yellow%20Fortress%20in%20Sarajevo%2C%20Bosnia%20and%20Herzegovina%2C%20in%20the%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699e77491fb3fcb426486672%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223213%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EShe's%20building%20her%20career%20in%20Sarajevo%2C%20Bosnia%20and%20Herzegovina.%3Cp%3EProvided%20by%20Macie%20Strum%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigur