0homegrown%20Flamingo%20missiles%20flew%20nearly%20900%20miles%20to%20strike%20an%20Iskander%20factory%20deep%20inside%20Russia%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227381%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Tomahawk%20missile%20is%20seen%20mounted%20on%20a%20factory%20platform.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699fcb1f1fb3fcb426487b4d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224920%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUkraine%20has%20been%20touting%20the%20Flamingo%20as%20an%20alternative%20or%20complement%20to%20the%20long-range%20Tomahawk.%3Cp%3EEfrem%20Lukatsky%2FAP%20Photo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EUkraine%20said%20last%20week%20that%20it%20used%20new%20Flamingo%20missiles%20to%20strike%20a%20factory%20deep%20inside%20Russia.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EZelenskyy%20now%20says%20that%20the%20locally%20made%20missiles%20flew%20almost%20900%20miles%20to%20hit%20their%20target.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Ukrainian%20president%20said%20that%20all%20of%20the%20missiles%20were%20able%20to%20survive%20Russian%20air%20defenses.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EUkrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelenskyy%20said%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20his%20country%20had%20struck%20a%20Russian%20military%20industrial%20plant%20with%20locally%20made%20cruise%20missiles%20that%20flew%20nearly%20900%20miles%20to%20reach%20their%20target.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkrainian%20officials%20earlier%20reported%20that%20the%20missile%20strike%20on%20Saturday%20had%20hit%20a%20plant%20in%20Votkinsk%2C%20an%20industrial%20town%20in%20Russia's%20Udmurt%20Republic%2C%20some%20860%20miles%20from%20the%20Ukrainian%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20carried%20out%20precise%20strikes%20with%20Flamingo%20missiles%20at%20a%20range%20of%201%2C400%20kilometers%2C%26quot%3B%20Zelenskyy%20said%20at%20a%20press%20conference%20in%20Kyiv.%20%26quot%3BI%20believe%20this%20is%20truly%20a%20success%20for%20our%20industry.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESuch%20an%20attack%20would%20be%20one%20of%20the%20longest-range%20strikes%20carried%20out%20so%20far%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-making-long-range-missile-flamingo-1000-kg-warhead-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Flamingo%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20touted%20as%20one%20of%20the%20star%20products%20in%20Ukraine's%20local%20defense%20manufacturing%20scene.%20Kyiv%20has%20been%20aggressively%20trying%20to%20expand%20its%20weapons%20industry%20as%20a%20complement%20to%20Western%20supplies%20and%20as%20a%20future%20export%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Flamingos'%20target%2C%20the%20Votkinsk%20plant%2C%20manufactures%20some%20of%20Russia's%20key%20munitions%2C%20such%20as%20ballistic%20missiles%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-mixes-missile-tactics-ukraine-feeds-intel-to-patriot-makers-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EIskander%20system%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20submarine-launched%20Bulava%20missile.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERussia%20has%20not%20officially%20confirmed%20that%20the%20factory%20was%20hit%2C%20but%20Alexander%20Brechalov%2C%20the%20governor%20of%20the%20Udmurt%20Republic%2C%20said%20on%20Saturday%20that%20an%20unspecified%20facility%20in%20the%20region%20had%20been%20attacked%20and%20three%20people%20were%20sent%20to%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrechalov%20did%20not%20say%20if%20the%20Flamingo%20was%20used%2C%20but%20warned%20against%20drone%20threats%20over%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkrainian%20open-source%20groups%20later%20published%20satellite%20images%20that%20appeared%20to%20show%20damage%20to%20one%20of%20the%20workshops%20at%20the%20Votkinsk%20factory%2C%20with%20a%20gaping%20hole%20in%20its%20roof%20and%20signs%20of%20fire%20damage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftelegram.org%2Fjs%2Ftelegram-widget.js%3F22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%