%22Olympic%20skier%20Alex%20Hall.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699e50c750f42603b0f8d7e6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%229504%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOlympic%20skier%20Alex%20Hall.%3Cp%3EProvided%20by%20Rao's%20Homemade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20is%20an%20as-told-to%20essay%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Alex%20Hall%2C%20an%20American%20freestyle%20skier%20and%20two-time%20Olympic%20medalist.%20He%20spoke%20with%20Business%20Insider%20as%20part%20of%20his%20partnership%20with%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.raos.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ERao's%20Homemade%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%20This%20story%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20born%20in%20Alaska%2C%20but%20grew%20up%20in%20Zurich.%20I%20started%20skiing%20when%20I%20was%203%2C%20and%20began%20freeskiiing%20by%2010.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20was%2015%2C%20I%20moved%20to%20Utah%20after%20being%20accepted%20to%20Park%20City%20Winter%20Sports%20School%2C%20and%20I've%20been%20based%20in%20Salt%20Lake%20City%20ever%20since.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpower-hours-day-in-the-life-successful-business-leaders-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPower%20Hours%3C%2Fa%3E%20series%20gives%20readers%20an%20inside%20look%20at%20how%20powerful%20leaders%20in%20business%20structure%20their%20workday.%20Reach%20out%20to%20editor%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Flauryn-haas%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELauryn%20Haas%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20share%20your%20daily%20routine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20days%2C%20I'm%20rarely%20in%20one%20place%20for%20long%2C%20since%20I%20spend%20most%20of%20the%20year%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvisited-every-country-best-cities-sydney-valletta-krabi-worst-delhi-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etraveling%20around%20the%20world%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20training%20camps%20and%20competitions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20what%20a%20typical%20training%20day%20looks%20like.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ef0647eb-9c2b-4a7c-8065-9466c9945541%5C%22%3EI%20usually%20wake%20up%20at%20around%207%20a.m.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20definitely%20an%20alarm%20guy%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20hit%20snooze.%20I%20stop%20my%20alarm%20and%20get%20my%20day%20going.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20funny%2C%20even%20on%20days%20when%20I%20can%20sleep%20in%2C%20I%20still%20have%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-analog-alarm-clock-stopped-doomscrolling-improved-mornings-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eset%20an%20alarm%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I'm%20not%20someone%20who%20can%20sleep%20that%20much%20anyway%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20like%20the%20idea%20of%20sleeping%20through%20the%20day.%20If%20I%20don't%20set%20one%2C%20I%20feel%20weird%20going%20to%20bed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20try%20not%20to%20stay%20on%20my%20phone%20for%20too%20long%20in%20bed%20and%20waste%20time.%20I'm%20pretty%20good%20about%20not%20spending%20a%20crazy%20amount%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-no-smartphone-social-media-friends-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etime%20on%20social%20media%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20so%20I'll%20quickly%20reply%20to%20some%20texts%20right%20when%20I%20get%20up%2C%20and%20maybe%20watch%20one%20or%20two%20videos.%20After%20that%2C%20I%20get%20my%20day%20going.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d65b60cd-a2b8-4dab-86fa-04b2e871c8b9%5C%22%3EFor%20breakfast%2C%20my%20teammates%20and%20I%20rotate%20cooking%20duties%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20eight%20guys%20on%20my%20freeski%20team%2C%20and%20two%20of%20us%20make%20food%20for%20everyone%20each%20morning.%20If%20it's%20your%20turn%20to%20make%20breakfast%2C%20you're%20up%20about%20half%20an%20hour%20earlier%20than%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pairing%20is%20mostly%20random%2C%20but%20there's%20a%20little%20strategy%20involved.%20We%20try%20to%20match%20someone%20who's%20good%20at%20cooking%20with%20someone%20who's%20not.%20We%20avoid%20putting%20two%20bad%20cooks%20together%20because%20then%20we%20know%20the%20meal%20won't%20be%20great.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsually%2C%20we'll%20make%20a%20big%20scramble%20with%20veggies%2C%20eggs%2C%20and%20bacon.%20I%20typically%20have%20a%20bowl%20of%20cereal%20on%20top%20of%20that%2C%20and%20then%20some%20orange%20juice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20not%20a%20huge%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdaily-routines-successful-business-people-share-power-hours-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebreakfast%20person%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20so%20I%20kind%20of%20have%20to%20force%20it%20down.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI'm%20pretty%20tired%20in%20the%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223d5f7b24-8346-4e24-81bf-2d3bb44cc933%5C%22%3EWe%20get%20all%20our%20gear%20together%20and%20hit%20the%20slopes%20around%208%3A30%20a.m.%20to%209%20a.m.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20warming%20up%2C%20we'll%20ski%20pretty%20much%20all%20day%20from%20about%2010%20a.m.%20until%203%20or%204%20p.m.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Alex%20Hall%20at%20Slopeski%20final%20at%20Milan%20Winter%20Olympics.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699e7fd9e8408f66718035c6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHall%20spends%20most%20of%20his%20day%20on%20the%20slopes.%3Cp%3EIan%20MacNicol%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20the%20guy%20who%20doesn't%20pay%20to%20get%20service%20when%20I'm%20traveling%20outside%20the%20US.%20I%20don't%20have%20an%20international%20plan%2C%20so%20my%20phone%20only%20works%20when%20I%20have%20WiFi.%20That%20means%20once%20I%20leave%20the%20house%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20I'm%20basically%20offline%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20day%20until%20the%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20can%20be%20a%20little%20annoying%20for%20someone%20back%20home%20who's%20trying%20to%20reach%20me%2C%20but%20for%20the%20most%20part%2C%20it's%20pretty%20nice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20people%20ski%20with%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fimpossible-to-break-phone-addiction-iphone-required-apps-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ephones%20in%20their%20pockets%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20listen%20to%20music%20or%20check%20messages%20between%20their%20runs.%20I%20just%20leave%20mine%20in%20my%20backpack%20so%20I%20don't%20get%20distracted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cf092ebe-b2a0-4cb3-b1ae-7b1c100e1dac%5C%22%3EI%20don't%20usually%20eat%20a%20full%20lunch%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I'm%20training%20really%20hard%20and%20then%20sit%20down%20for%20half%20an%20hour%20to%20eat%20a%20full%20meal%2C%20I%20find%20it%20hard%20to%20get%20motivated%20again%20in%20the%20afternoon.%20I'd%20rather%20keep%20the%20momentum%20going.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsually%2C%20I'll%20just%20take%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-productivity-hack-daily-routine-5-minute-slots-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efive-minute%20break%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20drink%20a%20bunch%20of%20water%2C%20and%20have%20two%20granola%20bars.%20Sometimes%20I'll%20pack%20a%20sandwich%20and%20eat%20it%20fast%2C%20then%20get%20right%20back%20out%20there.%20I'd%20rather%20finish%20a%20little%20earlier%20than%20take%20a%20long%20lunch%20and%20struggle%20to%20warm%20up%20again%20after%20having%20a%20big%20meal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we're%20done%20skiing%2C%20we%20head%20back%20down%20for%20a%20video%20review.%20We%20watch%20clips%20of%20our%20tricks%20and%20take%20notes%20on%20where%20we%20can%20improve.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224374%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Olympic%20skier%20Alex%20Hall.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699fb413e8408f6671804a19%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222917%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHall%20won%20silver%20in%20men's%20freestyle%20skiing%20slopestyle%20at%20the%202026%20Winter%20Olympics.%3Cp%3EPatrick%20Smith%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20that%2C%20we%20do%20a%20short%20recovery%20session%20with%20stretching%2C%20some%20time%20on%20the%20spin%20bike%2C%20and%20a%20bit%20of%20core%20work.%20It's%20usually%20no%20more%20than%20an%20hour.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22555f2a28-95dc-4b1e-9908-c92cb2a338e0%5C%22%3EIf%20the%20weather's%20nice%20and%20we%20still%20have%20some%20energy%2C%20we'll%20stay%20outside%20a%20bit%20longer%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDepending%20on%20where%20we%20are%2C%20we'll%20play%20a%20game%2C%20kick%20a%20soccer%20ball%2C%20or%20throw%20a%20football%20around%20in%20the%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20that%2C%20it's%20dinner%20time.%20Just%20like%20breakfast%2C%20two%20people%20are%20in%20charge%20of%20cooking%2C%20and%20we%20rotate%20through.%20I%20try%20not%20to%20eat%20too%20much%20of%20it%2C%20but%20I%20do%20love%20dessert%2C%20especially%20chocolate%20or%20ice%20cream.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe'll%20take%20some%20time%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Ffavorite-sleep-products%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eevening%20to%20relax%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20like%20watch%20TV%20or%20just%20hang%20out%20before%20bed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20use%20this%20time%20to%20complete%20my%20coursework.%20I%20major%20in%20environmental%20and%20sustainability%20studies%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Utah%2C%20and%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcollege-student-online-classes-traveling-world-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eclasses%20are%20online%3C%2Fa%3E%20since%20I%20travel%20so%20much.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20only%20take%20one%20or%20two%20classes%20at%20a%20time%2C%20so%20it's%20not%20every%20evening%20%E2%80%94%20usually%20it's%20every%20other%20evening.%20I'll%20do%20a%20half%20hour%20or%20an%20hour%2C%20depending%20on%20what%20I%20have%20to%20get%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere've%20been%20times%20when%20I've%20stayed%20up%20an%20extra%20hour%20or%20two%20the%20night%20before%20a%20competition%20to%20finish%20an%20assignment.%20But%20that's%20on%20me%20for%20procrastinating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d022e88a-5db8-43ef-8310-472417b5c4a9%5C%22%3EI%20try%20to%20go%20to%20sleep%20around%2011%20p.m.%20and%20avoid%20staying%20up%20past%20midnight%20if%20I%20can%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20like%20sleeping%20with%20the%20window%20open%20because%20I%20hate%20being%20too%20warm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20get%20about%20seven%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-tech-next-big-rival-sleep-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eeight%20hours%20of%20sleep%3C%2Fa%3E%20every%20night%2C%20and%20a%20bad%20night's%20sleep%20can%20really%20affect%20my%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20drink%20coffee%20or%20caffeine%2C%20so%20if%20I%20don't%20sleep%20much%2C%20I%20definitely%20feel%20it%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20though%20I%20usually%20shake%20it%20off%20after%20a%20couple%20of%20hours.%20If%20it's%20been%20a%20long%20week%20of%20training%2C%20bad%20sleep%20can%20sometimes%20make%20me%20feel%20less%20motivated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20usually%20fall%20asleep%20easily.%20It's%20more%20like%20I%20wake%20up%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20night%20sometimes.%20Lately%2C%20I've%20been%20traveling%20with%20my%20own%20pillow%20more%20often%2C%20based%20on%20a%20suggestion%20from%20some%20of%20my%20teammates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20there's%20space%20in%20my%20suitcase%2C%20I'll%20smash%20a%20pillow%20in%20there%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it%20usually%20helps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20pretty%20lucky%20that%20I%20love%20what%20I%20do.%20If%20I'm%20having%20doubts%20or%20a%20down%20day%2C%20I%20think%20about%20the%20fact%20that%20I%20get%20to%20do%20this%20surrounded%2