ew%20Anduril's%20YFQ-44A%20aircraft%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20a%20test%20over%20the%20Mojave%20Desert.%3Cp%3EShield%20AI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EShield%20AI's%20Hivemind%20AI%20program%20piloted%20Anduril's%20YFQ-44A%20uncrewed%20aircraft%20for%20the%20first%20time.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHivemind%20was%20selected%20earlier%20to%20provide%20autonomy%20for%20the%20Air%20Force's%20drone%20wingmen.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Air%20Force%20program%20is%20building%20uncrewed%20aircraft%20designed%20to%20fly%20with%20crewed%20fighter%20jets.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EShield%20AI's%20artificial%20intelligence%20pilot%20has%20flown%20one%20of%20the%20US%20Air%20Force's%20next-generation%20drone%20wingman%20contenders%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20the%20company%20announced%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshield-ai-new-aircraft-x-bat-autonomy-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EShield%20AI's%20Hivemind%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20same%20AI%20program%20that%20previously%20went%20head-to-head%20with%20a%20crewed%20fighter%20aircraft%20in%20aerial%20combat%2C%20was%20picked%20by%20the%20Air%20Force%20for%20autonomy%20testing%20as%20part%20of%20its%20Collaborative%20Combat%20Aircraft%2C%20or%20CCA%2C%20effort%20earlier%20this%20month.%20Now%2C%20it%20has%20flown%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanduril-fury-general-atomics-us-air-force-commercial-parts-engine-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAnduril's%20CCA%20competitor%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20achievement%20for%20the%20software%20that%20could%20pilot%20future%20uncrewed%20aircraft%20built%20to%20fly%20and%20fight%20alongside%20crewed%20US%20combat%20aircraft.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20defense%20company%20said%20Hivemind%2C%20piloting%20Anduril's%20Fury%20drone%2C%20also%20known%20as%20YFQ-44A%2C%20completed%20its%20first%20flight%20test%20over%20the%20Mojave%20Desert.%20The%20AI%20pilot%20met%20all%20required%20test%20points%2C%20including%20mid-mission%20updates%20and%20basic%20operational%20maneuvers%2C%20the%20company%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20successful%20test%20opens%20the%20door%20for%20expanded%20mission%20autonomy%20testing%20with%20Hivemind%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faffordable-ai-military-drones-shield-ai-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EShield%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20flight%20test%20showcases%20the%20potential%20of%20airpower%20built%20on%20mission%20autonomy%2C%26quot%3B%20Christian%20Gutierrez%2C%20vice%20president%20of%20Hivemind%20Solutions%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAcross%20platforms%2C%20domains%2C%20and%20environments%2C%20Hivemind%20provides%20resilient%20mission%20autonomy%2C%20proving%20that%20software%20is%20central%20to%20the%20future%20of%20airpower%2C%26quot%3B%20Gutierrez%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3Bour%20collaboration%20with%20Anduril%20reflects%20a%20new%20era%20of%20defense%20acquisition%2C%20where%20autonomy%20is%20treated%20as%20a%20foundational%20warfighting%20capability%20on%20par%20with%20the%20aircraft%20itself.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShield%20AI%20has%20spent%20more%20than%20a%20decade%20developing%20Hivemind's%20AI%20software%2C%20which%20is%20designed%20to%20perform%20many%20of%20the%20tasks%20of%20a%20human%20pilot.%20Unlike%20autopilot%20or%20other%20autonomous%20features%2C%20Hivemind%20is%20built%20to%20make%20real-time%20decisions%2C%20adjusting%20flight%20routes%20depending%20on%20conditions%20or%20obstacles%20to%20continue%20a%20mission%2C%20the%20company%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20AI%20software%20was%20used%20in%20the%20Air%20Force's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-militarys-ai-fighter-jet-pilot-making-dramatic-advances-officer-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI-enabled%20X-62A%20VISTA%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20modified%20F-16%20that%20flew%20simulated%20dogfights%20against%20a%20crewed%20fighter%20aircraft%20in%202024.%20The%20service%20has%20not%20publicly%20revealed%20which%20aircraft%20emerged%20victorious%20in%20those%20engagements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHivemind%20is%20also%20the%20AI%20pilot%20behind%20Shield%20AI's%20new%20X-BAT%20fighter%20aircraft%2C%20which%20the%20company%20unveiled%20in%20October.%20Shield%20AI%20says%20that%20the%20X-BAT%20can%20operate%20without%20human%20intervention%20and%20take%20off%20without%20runways%2C%20as%20well%20as%20in%20contested%20environments%20where%20GPS%20and%20reliable%20communications%20might%20not%20be%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnduril's%20Fury%20aircraft%20is%20one%20of%20the%20competitors%20for%20the%20CCA%20program%2C%20a%20priority%20of%20the%20Air%20Force%20that%20envisions%20uncrewed%20aircraft%20operating%20alongside%20crewed%20aircraft%20with%20some%20mixture%20of%20autonomy%20and%20human%20direction.%20Earlier%20this%20month%2C%20a%20test%20flight%20saw%20a%20CCA%20stand-in%20aircraft%20communicate%20and%20fly%20with%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-air-force-f22-mq20-drone-mock-combat-autonomy-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAir%20Force%20F-22%20Raptor%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20marking%20another%20step%20forward%20in%20the%20CCA%20program.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20Col.%20Timothy%20Helfrich%2C%20the%20Air%20Force's%20portfolio%20acquisition%20executive%20in%20fighters%20and%20advanced%20aircraft%2C%20commended%20the%20speed%20of%20work%20being%20done%20on%20autonomous%20pilots%20flying%20CCAs.%20%26quot%3BQuite%20an%20accomplishment%20going%20so%20quickly%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20at%20a%20panel%2C%20%26quot%3Bbut%20we've%20got%20a%20lot%20ahead%20of%20us%20though.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshield-ai-hivemind-flew-anduril-drone-wingman-aircraft-2026-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772056116000%