-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EI%20was%20vibe%20coding%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20alpha%20version%20of%20my%20product%2C%20I%20would%20hit%20spots%20where%2030%20or%2040%25%20would%20be%20wrong.%20I%20didn't%20know%20what%20exactly%20the%20problem%20was.%20I%20would%20have%20multiple%20screens%20running%20the%20code%20to%20figure%20it%20out%2C%20and%20I'd%20continue%20to%20use%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenclaw-ai-demand-token-use-surge-nvidia-pricing-jumps-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20against%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20until%20I%20could%20get%20to%20about%2095%25%20confidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20contracted%20a%20few%20developers%20to%20help%20move%20my%20product%20forward.%20Now%20I%20have%20a%20product%20developing%20at%20a%20faster%2C%20much%20more%20robust%2C%20and%20scalable%20rate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20much%20as%20I%20can%20do%20with%20AI%2C%20it's%20amazing%20what%20technical%20people%20can%20do%20with%20AI%20tools%20that%20a%20non-technical%20person%20can't.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f4b8c702-a7ff-4e61-a809-326f23388b73%5C%22%3EThe%20human%20perspective%20is%20still%20irreplaceable%20in%20my%20business%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20reached%20out%20to%20a%20lot%20of%20informal%20mentors%20and%20friends%20in%20the%20space%20who%20could%20be%20helpful%20early%20on%20in%20my%20process%2C%20but%20recently%20I%20formalized%20having%20advisors%20to%20bounce%20things%20off%20of.%20That%20has%20been%20a%20huge%20feather%20in%20my%20cap.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20advisors%20have%20their%20own%20expertise%20to%20draw%20on%2C%20and%20they%20know%20many%20smart%20people%20in%20this%20space%20working%20on%20projects%20that%20have%20helped%20us%20identify%20potential%20blind%20spots.%20It's%20helped%20me%20connect%20with%20potential%20partners%20in%20ways%20that%20I%20think%20would%20be%20more%20difficult%20as%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsolo-founder-runs-company-with-15-ai-agents-heres-