%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Econtent%20creator%20and%20blogger%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20originally%20from%20Canada%2C%20who%20hosts%20three%20Airbnbs%20in%20Puerto%20Vallarta%2C%20Mexico.%20Pope%20was%20away%20during%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpuerto-vallarta-tourism-boom-cartel-violence-americans-rethinking-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%20the%20violence%20in%20Jalisco%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20but%20was%20still%20in%20contact%20with%20her%20guests.%20The%20conversation%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPuerto%20Vallarta%20is%20my%20home%20base.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20went%20there%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%202021%20while%20I%20was%20a%20full-time%20digital%20nomad.%20In%202023%2C%20I%20bought%20an%20apartment%20in%20Puerto%20Vallarta%20and%20obtained%20residency%2C%20but%20I%20still%20travel%20for%20about%206%20months%20of%20the%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20own%20a%20one-bedroom%20condo%20that%20I%20rent%20out%20when%20I'm%20traveling%2C%20but%20I%20also%20have%20some%20long-term%20properties%20that%20I%20rent%20and%20then%20sublease%20on%20Airbnb%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-i-made-six-figures-renting-airbnb-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eit's%20called%20Airbnb%20arbitrage%3C%2Fa%3E.%20You%20rent%20them%2C%20then%20sublease%20them%20with%20the%20owner's%20permission.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20manage%20the%20Airbnb%20accounts%20and%20handle%20all%20guest%20messaging%3B%20everything%20falls%20under%20my%20purview.%20I%20just%20pay%20rent%20to%20the%20landlord%20every%20month.%20I%20started%20that%20in%20May%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20condo%20living%20room%20in%20Mexico.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699f2a201fb3fcb426486e01%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPope's%20condo%20in%20Puerto%20Vallarta.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Lora%20Pope.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20actually%20in%20Mexico%20City%20during%20the%20recent%20violence%2C%20so%20I%20wasn't%20there%20during%20the%20event.%20Still%2C%20all%20my%20places%20are%20booked%20out%20right%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ce0d6cf7-63e8-4bd7-8437-6a86fb0ec8bd%5C%22%3EI%20tried%20my%20best%20to%20give%20my%20guests%20all%20the%20information%20I%20had%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20woke%20up%20Sunday%20morning%2C%20I%20had%20a%20ton%20of%20messages%20from%20my%20friends%20in%20Puerto%20Vallarta%20showing%20videos%20of%20the%20explosions.%20I%20wasn't%20too%20sure%20what%20was%20happening%20because%20there%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20information%20coming%20quite%20rapidly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20waited%20a%20few%20hours%20to%20gather%20more%20information%20about%20what%20was%20happening.%20I%20was%20already%20receiving%20some%20messages%20from%20guests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20them%20was%20obviously%20alarmed.%20I%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20other%20two%20just%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20they%20were%20OK.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20that%20point%2C%20there%20were%20a%20lot%20of%20rumors%20running%20around%2C%20and%20people%20were%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BDon't%20go%20outside.%20They're%20threatening%20civilians.%26quot%3B%20I%20don't%20even%20think%20that%20was%20an%20official%20thing%2C%20but%20just%20to%20be%20safe%2C%20I%20told%20my%20guests%2C%20%26quot%3BPlease%20stay%20inside.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20lot%20of%20people%20were%20asking%20me%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20is%20your%20opinion%3F%20What%20do%20you%20think%3F%20What%20should%20we%20do%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20the%20thing%20people%20were%20most%20concerned%20about%20was%20food%2C%20because%2C%20obviously%2C%20people%20are%20on%20vacation%2C%20and%20they%20hadn't%20stocked%20up%20the%20kitchen%2C%20knowing%20that%20was%20going%20to%20happen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20kitchen%20in%20an%20Airbnb%20in%20Mexico.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699f2b18e8408f6671803d51%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOne%20of%20Pope's%20Airbnb%20properties%20in%20the%20Cinco%20de%20Diciembre%20neighborhood%20of%20Puerto%20Vallarta%2C%20Mexico.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Lora%20Pope.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20filtered%20water%20in%20all%20of%20my%20apartments%2C%20so%20I%20knew%20they%20had%20water%2C%20but%20I%20was%20mainly%20concerned%20about%20whether%20they%20had%20to%20stay%20inside%20for%20days%2C%20and%20if%20they%20could%20get%20by.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELuckily%2C%20all%20of%20them%20had%20enough%20food%20for%20that%20day.%20And%20by%20Monday%2C%20things%20had%20already%20calmed%20down%20a%20lot%2C%20and%20the%20grocery%20stores%20opened%20up%2C%20so%20they%20were%20able%20to%20get%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20thought%20more%20about%20natural%20disasters%20because%20we%20have%20had%20earthquakes%20or%20bad%20hurricanes%20in%20the%20past%2C%20but%20I've%20never%20thought%20about%20something%20like%20this%20because%20Puerto%20Vallarta%20has%20historically%20been%20one%20of%20the%20safest%20places%20in%20Mexico.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20sharing%20any%20official%20information%20I%20had%20from%20the%20municipality%2C%20trying%20to%20help%20my%20guests%20stay%20as%20calm%20as%20possible%2C%20and%20just%20letting%20them%20know%20I%20was%20there.%20And%20if%20they%20needed%20anything%2C%20I%20would%20do%20my%20best%20to%20get%20it.%20It%20was%20a%20pretty%20stressful%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhenever%20I%20travel%2C%20I%20always%20have%20someone%20in%20Puerto%20Vallarta%20as%20my%20backup%20%E2%80%94%20like%20an%20emergency%20contact.%20And%20she%20offered%20to%20do%20what%20she%20could%20to%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fa4c7f66-ff96-4922-a6a6-d6564dea0b4c%5C%22%3EI've%20already%20had%20a%20few%20cancellations%2C%20but%20I'm%20hoping%20this%20doesn't%20crush%20the%20long-term%20tourism%20economy%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20properties%20are%20very%20much%20in%20affected%20areas.%20As%20far%20as%20I%20know%2C%20I%20haven't%20had%20any%20reports%20of%20damage%20to%20my%20properties.%20Everything%20has%20been%20good.%20I've%20been%20in%20constant%20contact%20with%20my%20neighbors.%20I%20don't%20think%20the%20intention%20was%20to%20harm%20civilians.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20guests%20that%20I%20currently%20have%20have%20not%20talked%20about%20leaving%20early.%20The%20first%20day%2C%20I%20think%20there%20were%20a%20lot%20of%20flights%20being%20canceled%2C%20so%20it%20was%20quite%20difficult%20to%20leave%20early.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20it%20seems%20like%20flights%20are%20resuming.%20My%20guest%20in%20Cinco%20actually%20reached%20out%20Monday%2C%20saying%20they%20were%20worried%20about%20their%20flight%20being%20canceled%20and%20asking%20if%20the%20apartment%20was%20available%20to%20stay%20longer%20if%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20had%20a%20few%20cancellations%20for%20future%20bookings%2C%20though.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20one%20guest%2C%20who%20was%20supposed%20to%20check%20in%20on%20Wednesday%20at%20the%20Zona%20Rom%C3%A1ntica%20apartment%2C%20reach%20out%20on%20Monday%20to%20ask%20me%20for%20my%20opinion%20on%20the%20situation%20and%20whether%20it%20was%20safe%20to%20travel%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20hallway%20in%20an%20Airbnb%20property%20in%20Puerto%20Vallarta%2C%20Mexico.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699f2b6b50f42603b0f8e1b5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAnother%20Airbnb%20property%20hosted%20by%20Pope.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Lora%20Pope.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20there%20was%20still%20a%20lot%20of%20uncertainty%20about%20whether%20it%20would%20get%20better.%20She%20ended%20up%20canceling%20on%20Tuesday.%20Airbnb%20has%2C%20because%20it's%20considered%20a%20major%20disruptive%20event%2C%20waived%20the%20cancellation%20policy.%20So%20even%20if%20my%20cancellation%20policy%20says%20you%20must%20cancel%20within%20five%20days%2C%20Airbnb%20will%20waive%20the%20cancellation%20for%20them%2C%20given%20the%20circumstances.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20I've%20had%20three%20future%20cancellations%20%E2%80%94%20I%20would%20assume%20that%20those%20are%20due%20to%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20really%20hope%20this%20doesn't%20affect%20business%20down%20the%20line.%20I%20do%20think%20it's%20definitely%20going%20to%20have%20an%20immediate%20effect.%20I%20just%20know%20people%20can%20get%20really%20spooked%2C%20and%20there's%20already%20a%20lot%20of%20fearmongering%20that%20happens%20about%20Mexico.%20So%20I%20do%20think%20this%20is%20going%20to%20impact%20people's%20perceptions%20and%20maybe%20make%20them%20feel%20less%20safe%20coming%20here%2C%20which%20is%20really%20unfortunate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20what%20I've%20heard%2C%20Puerto%20Vallarta%20is%20already%20returning%20to%20normal%20%E2%80%94%20not%20that%20I'm%20minimizing%20what%20happened%20on%20Monday.%20As%20I%20said%2C%20Puerto%20Vallarta%20has%20always%20been%20one%20of%20the%20safest%20places%20in%20Mexico%20to%20live%20or%20visit.%20But%20I%20am%20definitely%20concerned%20about%20the%20immediate%20impact%20on%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20high%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20watching%20the%20sunset%20on%20the%20beach%20in%20Mexico.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699f28ffe8408f6671803d0d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPope%20in%20Puerto%20Vallarta%2C%20Mexico.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Lora%20Pope.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20properties%20are%20pretty%20important%20%E2%80%94%20they%20make%20up%20at%20least%20half%20my%20income.%20I%20am%20trying%20not%20to%20panic%20too%20much%20about%20the%20situation%20right%20now%20because%20it's%20so%20recent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20think%20it'll%20get%20to%20the%20point%20where%20I%20can't%20cover%20my%20rent%2C%20but%20it's%20definitely%20a%20scary%20thought%2C%20how%20much%20this%20is%20going%20to%20impact%20tourism.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20next%20year%2C%20I%20hope%20that%2C%20over%20the%20course%20of%20the%20year%2C%20as%20people%20see%20things%20are%20fine%20and%20visitors%20to%20Puerto%20Vallarta%20are%20having%20a%20good%20time%2C%20it'll%20fade%20from%20their%20memories%2C%20and%20we'll%20come%20back%20stronger.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20always%20been%20a%20really%20popular%20tourist%20destination%2C%20so%20I%20think%20in%20the%20long%20term%20it'll%20be%20OK.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAn%20Airbnb%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20monitoring%20this%20situation%20carefully%20and%20are%20focused%20on%20supporting%20guests%20and%20hosts%20in%20impacted%20areas.%20We%20have%20implemented%20our%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.airbnb.com%2Fan-update-on-our-major-disruptive-events-policy%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EMajor%20Disruptive%20Events%20Policy%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20in%20the%20entirety%20of%20Jalisco%2C%20as%20well%20as%20other%20impacted%20regions%2C%20providing%20cancellation%20and%20refund%20support.%20We%20encourage%20any%20members%20of%20our%20community%20who%20need%20assistance%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20our%2024%2F7%20support%20team.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fairbnb-host-puerto-vallarta-tourism-picks-back-up-2026-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772048479000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699f28361fb3fcb426486dbd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https