%20Summers%20says%20he%20is%20stepping%20back%20from%20public%20life.%3Cp%3EKevin%20Dietsch%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ELarry%20Summers%20is%20retiring%20from%20Harvard%20amid%20Epstein%20email%20fallout%20and%20ongoing%20investigations.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EEmails%20reveal%20Larry%20Summers%20sought%20advice%20from%20Jeffrey%20Epstein%20on%20a%20romantic%20relationship.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHarvard%20is%20continuing%20to%20investigate%20Summers'%20ties%20to%20Epstein.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFormer%20US%20Treasury%20Secretary%20and%20Harvard%20University%20President%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flarry-summers-stepping-away-public-life-epstein-emails-harvard-work-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ELarry%20Summers%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20leaving%20his%20position%20as%20a%20professor%20at%20the%20elite%20university%2C%20he%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20made%20the%20difficult%20decision%20to%20retire%20from%20my%20Harvard%20professorship%20at%20the%20end%20of%20this%20academic%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20Summers%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20%26quot%3BI%20will%20always%20be%20grateful%20to%20the%20thousands%20of%20students%20and%20colleagues%20I%20have%20been%20privileged%20to%20teach%20and%20work%20with%20since%20coming%20to%20Harvard%20as%20a%20graduate%20student%2050%20years%20ago.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20retirement%20is%20the%20latest%20fallout%20for%20Summers%20over%20his%20relationship%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fepstein-files-consequences-resignations-brad-karp-kathy-ruemmler-wasserman%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Enow-dead%20sex%20offender%20Jeffrey%20Epstein.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFiles%20released%20by%20the%20Justice%20Department%20and%20House%20Oversight%20Committee%20in%20recent%20months%20shed%20new%20light%20on%20Summers'%20relationship%20with%20Epstein%2C%20who%20died%20in