5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222040%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20talked%20to%20fire%20safety%20experts%20and%20tested%2010%20alarms%20in%20my%20own%20home%20to%20find%20the%20most%20reliable%20smoke%20detectors%20on%20the%20market.%3Cp%3EJanelle%20Leeson%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20most%20modern%20households%2C%20we've%20filled%20our%20home%20with%20synthetic%2C%20petroleum-based%20materials%2C%20from%20our%20couch%20cushions%20to%20our%20daughter's%20toys.%20These%20everyday%20products%20make%20house%20fires%20burn%20faster%20than%20ever%2C%20says%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fin%2Fsusan-mckelvey-6723942b%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESusan%20McKelvey%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nfpa.org%2FNFPA-Solutions%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENational%20Fire%20Protection%20Association%20(NFPA)%3C%2Fa%3E.%20She%20says%20that%20I%20may%20have%20as%20little%20as%20one%20to%20two%20minutes%20to%20get%20my%20family%20out%20once%20a%20smoke%20alarm%20sounds.%20With%20such%20a%20narrow%20window%2C%20one%20of%20the%20best%20smoke%20detectors%20is%20non-negotiable%20for%20my%20family's%20safety.%20The%20best%20smoke%20alarm%20strikes%20a%20delicate%20balance%20between%20sensitivity%20and%20reliability%2C%20giving%20us%20precious%20time%20to%20escape%20in%20the%20case%20of%20a%20fire%20without%20triggering%20false%20alarms%20every%20time%20I%20cook.%20Some%20models%20also%20detect%20carbon%20monoxide%2C%20a%20deadly%2C%20odorless%20gas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20consulting%20with%20three%20fire%20safety%20experts%20%E2%80%94%20including%20McKelvey%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fin%2Fbrian-sayles-89b87b321%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBrian%20Sayles%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20fire%20marshal%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lanefire.org%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELane%20Fire%20Authority%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%