ED-IMAGE-2025-08-31T222111.433-1756659080-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-494325%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EBright%2C%20vibrant%2C%20and%20fragrant%2C%20marigolds%20were%20indispensable%20for%20garlands%2C%20temple%20offerings%2C%20and%20door%20hangings.%20Image%20courtesy%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.shutterstock.com%2Fimage-photo%2Fold-indian-woman-planting-young-tree-2453636497%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EShutterstock%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20gardens%20were%20living%20spaces%20with%20purpose%2C%20where%20flowers%20brightened%20homes%2C%20aided%20in%20worship%2C%20or%20offered%20medicine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20legacy%20we%20carry%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20many%20of%20us%20live%20in%20apartments%20where%20balconies%20replace%20courtyards.%20Yet%20the%20sight%20of%20a%20pot%20brimming%20with%20orange%20marigolds%20still%20brings%20comfort.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPlanting%20them%20in%20October%20is%20more%20than%20gardening%20%E2%80%94%20it%20is%20keeping%20tradition%20alive.%20It%20is%20remembering%20how%20grandmothers%20understood%20seasons%20by%20watching%20the%20sky%2C%20soil%2C%20and%20festivals%20rather%20than%20apps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20plant%20marigolds%20now%20is%20to%20inherit%20their%20wisdom%3A%20to%20let%20gardens%20breathe%20colour%2C%20protect%20other%20plants%20naturally%2C%20and%20welcome%20a%20flower%20that%20has%20walked%20with%20Indian%20households%20for%20centuries.%20When%20October%20comes%2C%20pressing%20a%20few%20marigold%20seeds%20into%20the%20soil%20may%20remind%20you%20why%20your%20grandmother%20always%20did%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20grow%20marigolds%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20don%E2%80%99t%20let%20your%20grandmother%E2%80%99s%