his%20delicate%2C%20niche%20quality%20and%20connects%20them%20back%20to%20their%20heritage.%20They%20also%20appreciate%20the%20custom%20options%2C%20different%20flowers%2C%20pearls%2C%20and%20colour%20schemes%2C%20which%20allow%20them%20to%20personalise%20in%20a%20way%20fresh%20flowers%20often%20can%E2%80%99t.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20single%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F335040%2Fgujarat-padma-pareekh-runs-pb-handmades-crochet-handicraft-small-business-senior-citizen%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecrochet%20%3Cem%3Evarmala%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3Etakes%20between%2014%20to%2020%20hours%20to%20complete%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20design.%20The%20process%20begins%20with%20careful%20planning%3A%20the%20right%20flower%20size%2C%20the%20right%20colours%2C%20the%20right%20balance%20of%20pearls%20and%20embellishments.%20Once%20the%20prototype%20is%20approved%2C%20her%20team%20of%2025%20underprivileged%20women%20artisans%20from%20Uttarakhand%20gets%20to%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETanya%20Setia%E2%80%99s%20Gul%20is%20another%20powerhouse%20of%20sustainability%20where%20beautiful%20crochet%20%3Cem%3Evarmalas%3C%2Fem%3E%20take%20shape.%20%E2%80%9CEach%20piece%20is%20a%20work%20of%20art%20that%20embodies%20the%20beauty%20of%20rural%20India%20and%20the%20passion%20of%20our%20women%20artisans.%20We%20at%20Gul%20Jaipur%20are%20firm%20believers%20in%20the%20virtues%20of%20conscious%20living%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Tanya.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20work%20closely%20with%20our%20women%20artisans%20to%20guarantee%20that%20they%20receive%20their%20much-deserved%20recognition%20and%20working%20conditions%20while%20creating%20our%20products%20using%20their%20learned%20skill%20sets%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%