a.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-08-26T191444.378_11zon-1756215895-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-492257%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMarigolds%20have%20bright%20yellow%20and%20orange%20petals%20that%20are%20rich%20in%20natural%20pigment%20and%20can%20be%20dried%20and%20ground%20into%20a%20fine%20powder%3B%20Picture%20source%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fagriplanting.com%2Fhow-to-grow-marigold-at-home%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EAgri%20Planting%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20their%20vibrant%20colour%2C%20marigolds%20are%20beneficial%20for%20the%20garden%20as%20they%20repel%20pests%20and%20attract%20pollinators.%20The%20flowers%20bloom%20generously%2C%20making%20them%20perfect%20for%20regular%20harvesting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E2.%20Hibiscus%20%E2%80%93%20Red%20and%20pink%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHibiscus%20is%20a%20hardy%2C%20tropical%20shrub%20known%20for%20its%20large%20and%20striking%20blooms%20in%20shades%20of%20red%2C%20pink%2C%20and%20occasionally%20white%20or%20yellow.%20It%20flowers%20throughout%20the%20year%20in%20warmer%20climates%20and%20prefers%20well-watered%20soil%20and%20plenty%20of%20sunlight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20make%20rangoli%20powder%2C%20the%20petals%20should%20be%20dried%20in%20the%20shade%20to%20preserve%20their%20colour%20before%20being%20ground%20to%20a%20fine%20consistency.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F473545%2Fgrow-hibiscus-in-balcony-guide-benefits%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHibiscus%20flowers%20also%20attract%20butterflies%20and%20bees%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20turning%20the%20garden%20into%20a%20lively%20and%20colourful%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3